O-GlcNAcylation of SIRT1 enhances its deacetylase activity and promotes 
cytoprotection under stress.

Han C(1)(2)(3), Gu Y(4)(5)(6)(7), Shan H(1)(8)(2)(3), Mi W(1)(2)(3), Sun 
